SELECT   l_orderkey,   o_orderdate,   c_name,   l_extendedprice,   l_discount FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey ORDER BY   l_orderkey;
SELECT   l_orderkey,   o_orderdate,   c_name FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey ORDER BY   l_orderkey;

SELECT SIN(l_quantity) + COS(l_extendedprice) + EXP(l_discount) + LOG(l_tax) + TAN(l_linestatus) FROM tpch1g.lineitem ;

SELECT SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(EXP(l_quantity))))) + COS(COS(COS(COS(EXP(l_extendedprice))))) + LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(EXP(l_discount))))) + EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_tax)))) FROM tpch1g.lineitem ;
SELECT     SUM(l_quantity) AS total_quantity,     SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extendedprice,     SUM(l_discount) AS total_discount FROM     tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT   SUM(EXP(LOG(l_quantity + 1))) AS exp_log_quantity,   SUM(SIN(COS(l_extendedprice))) AS sin_cos_extendedprice,   SUM(SUBSTRING(CAST(l_discount AS VARCHAR), 1, 2)) AS substring_discount FROM   tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT   SUM(EXP(LOG(l_quantity + 1))) AS exp_log_quantity,   SUM(SIN(COS(l_extendedprice))) AS sin_cos_extendedprice,   SUM(CAST(SUBSTRING(CAST(l_discount AS VARCHAR), 1, 2) AS DECIMAL)) AS substring_discount FROM   tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT   SUM(EXP(LOG(l_quantity + 1) * SIN(l_extendedprice))) AS complex_calculation,   SUM(COS(l_discount) * TAN(l_tax)) AS trigonometric_calculation,   SUM(LENGTH(CAST(l_comment AS VARCHAR))) AS comment_length FROM   tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT c_name, o_orderdate, l_extendedprice FROM tpch1g.customer JOIN tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey  ;

SELECT SIN(EXP(l_extendedprice)), SUBSTRING(c_name, 1, 5), DATE_ADD(o_orderdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) FROM tpch1g.customer JOIN tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey ;

SELECT SIN(EXP(l_extendedprice)), SUBSTRING(c_name, 1, 5), DATE_ADD(o_orderdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) FROM tpch1g.customer JOIN tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey JOIN tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN tpch1g.partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey AND s_suppkey = ps_suppkey ;

SELECT SIN(EXP(l_extendedprice)), SUBSTRING(c_name, 1, 5), DATE_ADD(o_orderdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) FROM tpch1g.customer JOIN tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey JOIN tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN tpch1g.partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey AND s_suppkey = ps_suppkey JOIN tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN tpch1g.region ON n_regionkey = r_regionkey ;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment  FROM tpch5g.lineitem  ORDER BY l_shipdate, l_orderkey;
SELECT c_custkey, c_name, c_address, c_phone, c_acctbal, c_mktsegment, c_comment FROM tpch5g.customer ORDER BY c_custkey;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment,     SIN(l_quantity) + COS(l_extendedprice) + LOG(l_discount + 1) AS complex_calculation FROM tpch5g.lineitem ORDER BY l_shipdate, l_orderkey;
SELECT o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderstatus, o_totalprice, o_orderdate, o_orderpriority, o_clerk, o_shippriority, o_comment FROM tpch5g.orders ORDER BY o_orderdate, o_orderkey;

SELECT     n_name,     SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM     tpch5g.customer JOIN     tpch5g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN     tpch5g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN     tpch5g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey GROUP BY     n_name;

SELECT   r_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch5g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch5g.region ON n_regionkey = r_regionkey GROUP BY   r_name;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * l_quantity) AS total_value FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch5g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey GROUP BY   n_name;

SELECT   c_nationkey,   SUM(l_extendedprice * l_discount) AS discount_revenue FROM   tpch5g.lineitem JOIN   tpch5g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch5g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey GROUP BY   c_nationkey;

SELECT     n_name,     SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM     tpch1g.lineitem JOIN     tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN     tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN     tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey WHERE     l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'     AND l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01'     AND n_name = 'GERMANY' GROUP BY     n_name;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * EXP(l_tax)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.lineitem JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey WHERE   l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'   AND l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01'   AND n_name = 'GERMANY'   AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey GROUP BY   n_name;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * EXP(l_tax) * LOG(l_quantity + 1)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.lineitem JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey WHERE   l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'   AND l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01'   AND n_name = 'GERMANY'   AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey GROUP BY   n_name;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * EXP(l_tax) * LOG(l_quantity + 1) * COS(l_extendedprice)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.lineitem JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN   tpch1g.partsupp ON l_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE   l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'   AND l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01'   AND n_name = 'GERMANY'   AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey GROUP BY   n_name;

SELECT SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(EXP(l_quantity)))), COS(COS(COS(COS(l_extendedprice)))), EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_discount)))), SUBSTRING(SUBSTRING(SUBSTRING(SUBSTRING(l_shipinstruct, 1, 5), 1, 5), 1, 5), 1, 5), CONCAT(CONCAT(CONCAT(l_returnflag, l_linestatus), l_returnflag), l_linestatus) FROM tpch1g.lineitem ;

SELECT      n_name,      l_year,      SUM(volume) AS revenue FROM (     SELECT          n_name,          EXTRACT(YEAR FROM o_orderdate) AS l_year,          l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) AS volume     FROM          tpch1g.customer,          tpch1g.orders,          tpch1g.lineitem,          tpch1g.supplier,          tpch1g.nation     WHERE          c_custkey = o_custkey          AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey          AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey          AND n_nationkey = c_nationkey          AND o_orderdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' ) AS all_nations GROUP BY      n_name,      l_year ORDER BY      n_name,      l_year DESC;

SELECT   c_name,   o_orderdate,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE   o_orderdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' GROUP BY   c_name,   o_orderdate ORDER BY   revenue DESC,   o_orderdate LIMIT 100;

SELECT   c_name,   o_orderdate,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * EXP(0.01 * l_quantity)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE   o_orderdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' GROUP BY   c_name,   o_orderdate ORDER BY   revenue DESC,   o_orderdate;

SELECT   c_name,   o_orderdate,   SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * EXP(0.01 * l_quantity)) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem l2 ON l2.l_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE   o_orderdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' GROUP BY   c_name,   o_orderdate ORDER BY   revenue DESC,   o_orderdate;

SELECT c_name, o_orderdate, l_extendedprice, l_discount FROM tpch1g.customer JOIN tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey  ;

SELECT   c_name,   o_orderdate,   l_extendedprice,   l_discount,   SIN(l_extendedprice) + COS(l_discount) AS complex_calc,   SUBSTRING(c_name, 1, 5) AS name_part,   DATE_ADD(o_orderdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) AS next_day FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey ;

SELECT   c_name,   o_orderdate,   l_extendedprice,   l_discount,   SIN(l_extendedprice) + COS(l_discount) AS complex_calc,   SUBSTRING(c_name, 1, 5) AS name_part,   DATE_ADD(o_orderdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) AS next_day FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey ;

SELECT  c_name,  o_orderdate,  l_extendedprice,  l_discount,  SIN(EXP(l_extendedprice)) + COS(EXP(l_discount)) AS complex_calc,  CONCAT(SUBSTRING(c_name, 1, 5), SUBSTRING(c_name, 6, 5)) AS name_part,  DATE_ADD(o_orderdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) AS next_day FROM  tpch1g.customer JOIN  tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN  tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN  tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey JOIN  tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN  tpch1g.lineitem li2 ON li2.l_orderkey = lineitem.l_orderkey ;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment  FROM tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT   EXP(l_quantity),   LOG(l_extendedprice),   SIN(l_discount),   COS(l_tax),   SUBSTRING(l_comment, 1, 10),   CONCAT(l_shipmode, l_shipinstruct),   DATE_ADD(l_shipdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY) FROM   tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT  EXP(SIN(COS(EXP(l_quantity)))),  LOG(EXP(SIN(l_extendedprice))),  SIN(COS(EXP(l_discount))),  COS(SIN(EXP(l_tax))),  SUBSTRING(CONCAT(l_comment, l_shipmode), 1, 20),  CONCAT(l_shipmode, l_shipinstruct, l_returnflag),  DATE_ADD(DATE_SUB(l_shipdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY), INTERVAL 2 DAY) FROM  tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT  EXP(SIN(COS(EXP(SIN(l_quantity))))),  LOG(EXP(SIN(COS(l_extendedprice)))),  SIN(COS(EXP(SIN(l_discount)))),  COS(SIN(EXP(COS(l_tax)))),  SUBSTRING(CONCAT(l_comment, l_shipmode, l_shipinstruct), 1, 30),  CONCAT(l_shipmode, l_shipinstruct, l_returnflag, l_linestatus),  DATE_ADD(DATE_SUB(DATE_ADD(l_shipdate, INTERVAL 1 DAY), INTERVAL 2 DAY), INTERVAL 3 DAY) FROM  tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax FROM tpch1g.lineitem JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey WHERE l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01' AND l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' AND o_orderstatus = 'F' AND l_discount BETWEEN 0.05 AND 0.07 AND l_quantity < 24;

SELECT l1.l_orderkey, l1.l_partkey, l1.l_suppkey, l1.l_quantity, l1.l_extendedprice,     SIN(EXP(l1.l_discount)) AS complex_calc,     CONCAT(o_orderpriority, o_clerk) AS combined_string FROM tpch1g.lineitem l1 JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l2 ON l1.l_orderkey = l2.l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l1.l_orderkey = o_orderkey WHERE l1.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01' AND l1.l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' AND o_orderstatus = 'F' AND l1.l_discount BETWEEN 0.05 AND 0.07 AND l1.l_quantity < 24;

SELECT l1.l_orderkey, l1.l_partkey, l1.l_suppkey, l1.l_quantity, l1.l_extendedprice,   SIN(EXP(l1.l_discount)) AS complex_calc,   CONCAT(o_orderpriority, o_clerk) AS combined_string,   DATE_ADD(l1.l_shipdate, INTERVAL l1.l_quantity DAY) AS new_shipdate FROM tpch1g.lineitem l1 JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l2 ON l1.l_orderkey = l2.l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l1.l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l1.l_partkey = p_partkey WHERE l1.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01' AND l1.l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' AND o_orderstatus = 'F' AND l1.l_discount BETWEEN 0.05 AND 0.07 AND l1.l_quantity < 24;

SELECT l1.l_orderkey, l1.l_partkey, l1.l_suppkey, l1.l_quantity, l1.l_extendedprice,  SIN(EXP(l1.l_discount)) AS complex_calc,  CONCAT(o_orderpriority, o_clerk) AS combined_string,  DATE_ADD(l1.l_shipdate, INTERVAL l1.l_quantity DAY) AS new_shipdate FROM tpch1g.lineitem l1 JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l2 ON l1.l_orderkey = l2.l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l1.l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part ON l1.l_partkey = p_partkey WHERE l1.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01' AND l1.l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' AND o_orderstatus = 'F' AND l1.l_discount BETWEEN 0.05 AND 0.07 AND l1.l_quantity < 24 AND p_brand = 'Brand#23';

SELECT * FROM tpch1g.lineitem, tpch1g.partsupp ;
SELECT * FROM tpch1g.lineitem, tpch1g.part ;

SELECT c.c_name, o.o_orderkey, l.l_partkey, l.l_quantity FROM tpch1g.customer c JOIN tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN tpch1g.partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey JOIN tpch1g.supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey JOIN tpch1g.nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN tpch1g.region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey;

SELECT   c.c_name,   o.o_orderkey,   l.l_partkey,   l.l_quantity,   SIN(EXP(l.l_extendedprice)) AS complex_calc,   CONCAT(c.c_name, p.p_name) AS combined_name,   DATE_ADD(o.o_orderdate, INTERVAL l.l_quantity DAY) AS new_date FROM tpch1g.customer c JOIN tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN tpch1g.partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey JOIN tpch1g.supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey JOIN tpch1g.nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN tpch1g.region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey;

SELECT   c.c_name,   o.o_orderkey,   l.l_partkey,   l.l_quantity,   SIN(EXP(l.l_extendedprice)) AS complex_calc,   CONCAT(c.c_name, p.p_name) AS combined_name,   DATE_ADD(o.o_orderdate, INTERVAL l.l_quantity DAY) AS new_date FROM tpch1g.customer c JOIN tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN tpch1g.partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey JOIN tpch1g.supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey JOIN tpch1g.nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN tpch1g.region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l2 ON l.l_orderkey = l2.l_orderkey;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(EXP(LOG(l_extendedprice) * (1 - l_discount))) AS complex_revenue FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN   tpch1g.partsupp ON l_partkey = ps_partkey GROUP BY   n_name;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * l_discount) AS revenue FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN   tpch1g.partsupp ON l_partkey = ps_partkey GROUP BY   n_name;

SELECT   n_name,   SUM(l_extendedprice * l_quantity) AS total_value FROM   tpch1g.customer JOIN   tpch1g.orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey JOIN   tpch1g.partsupp ON l_partkey = ps_partkey JOIN   tpch1g.part ON l_partkey = p_partkey GROUP BY   n_name;
